{\fs20 In situations in which people must make a decision about which of several alternative actions to perform:\par }\pard\plain \s25\f6\fs20\ltrpar\ql\fi-200\li370\ri0\sb60\sa0\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-1 Provide specific cues for them to use to \u173 ?reduce the number of \ldblquote stimulus choices\rdblquote  in the situation on which to base the decision.\par }
{\fs20 When it is possible to do so, provide specific advance information about which action will most likely need to be performed.\par }
\pard\plain \s24\f6\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb120\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20 When designing performance environments in }{\fs20 \line }{\fs20 which people will need to perform different movements to different stimuli, design the spatial relationship between the locations of the stimuli and their associated movements to be as spatially compatible as possible.\par }
{\fs20 If a person must perform a skill that requires him or her to initiate movement as quickly as possible to a specific \ldblquote go\rdblquote  command:}
{\fs20 \par }\pard\plain \s25\f6\fs20\ltrpar\ql\fi-200\li370\ri0\sb60\sa0\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20 Provide a warning signal, such as \ldblquote get ready,\rdblquote  before the command.}{\fs20 \par }{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0
Allow a brief amount of time between the warning and command signals, but don\rquote t make this interval of time so long that the \line person will not be optimally prepared to \line move on the command.}
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 \par }\pard\plain \s24\f6\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb120\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20 To obtain a reliable indication of how quickly a person can initiate movement to a specific command, have the person perform several successive repetitions of the activity and make the interval of time between the \ldblquote get ready\rdblquote  and }
{\fs20 \ldblquote go\rdblquote  signals different for each repetition.\par The degree of accuracy required by a movement will influence the amount of time a person needs to initiate the movement. Encourage the person to focus his or her movement preparation on the \u173 ?
accuracy demands imposed by the environmental context and not on the movements that will be performed.}{\fs20 \par }\pard\plain \s24\f6\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb120\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20 When teaching an athlete to fake movements to gain an advantage over an opponent, emphasize the need to perform the fake as convincingly as possible so that the opponent initiates movement in response to the fake and then to perform the \u173 ?
intended movement as soon as possible.\par }\pard\plain \s24\f6\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb120\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw1 When working with people who will perform skills in vigilance situations, provide strategies for them to take breaks from a sustained and continued maintenance of attention in the situation in which they must perform. These strategies will differ according to the demands of the situation}
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-1 .\par }\pard\plain \s24\f6\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb100\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
