performed. The muscles involved in the postural preparation process are as critical to the success of performing an activity as are the muscles \u173 ?
involved in performing the activity itself.}{\fs20 \par }\pard\plain \s26\f5\fs18\ltrpar\ql\fi0\li120\ri0\sb0\sa260\facenter\sl220\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\caps\b\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar0\lang1033
