 method): The participant pressed a }{\fs18 telegraph-type key as soon as possible with the right hand when the right light illuminated and with the left hand when the left light illuminated.\par }
{\f4\fs18\b0\i Discrimination reaction-time task}{\fs18  (Donders called this the }{\f4\fs18\b0\i c}{\fs18  method): The participant pressed a \u173 ?
telegraph-type key as soon as possible when a light of specified color illuminated, but not when any other light illuminated (e.g., respond to the red light, but not to the green light).\par }
